Data are prepared by Members of the World Meteorological Organization (WMO) for selected stations and exchanged monthly via international telecommunications. The publication has separate sections for surface and upper air observations, and is stored as a PDF file. These data includes surface parameters pressure, temperature, vapor pressure, precipitation, sunshine and upper level pressure, height, temperature, and winds.   </dct:description>
